	<call_out_content_html>&lt;h2 class="title--md no-margin-top" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: 32px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-style: italic; background-color: #02d2ff;"&gt;Alright, if you successfully ticked one of those boxes, that&amp;rsquo;s good news, but you&amp;rsquo;ve still got a few hurdles to jump through before you get a lower tax bill. Hey - we only said you don&amp;rsquo;t have to wear pants. We didn&amp;rsquo;t say that it would be easy.&lt;/h2&gt;</call_out_content_html>
