	<sectionContent_html>&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Working from home has its benefits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Apart from not having to wear pants all day, and not having to deal with annoying co-workers, you may also be able to claim for some tax deductions for the costs of setting up and running your home office. In this blog we listed all of the items that SARS will allow you to deduct from your tax bill, and we learned that you can claim tax breaks for your workspace itself against some of your property costs. Nice!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Now that you&amp;rsquo;re an expert on tax breaks while working from home, why not stick around and learn a bit more from our own financial guru, the lovely Nicolette Mashile? She recently hosted a masterclass called &amp;lsquo;3 steps to financial success&amp;rsquo; where she shares her proven formula to help you level up your money management skills. It&amp;rsquo;s available for you to check out right now for the grand total of: MAHALA!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a class="btn btn--primary" style="background-color: #e01f26; display: inline-flex; position: relative; white-space: nowrap; justify-content: center; text-decoration-line: none; line-height: 1; padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm); border-radius: var(--btn-radius); border-color: transparent; font-size: var(--btn-font-size); transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; min-width: 196px; min-height: 19px; align-items: center; color: #ffffff !important;" role="button" href="https://event.webinarjam.com/register/146/pl388f6m" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Register for free&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
